Audience Member: When
are you speaking at TED?

01:22:55.890 --> 01:22:59.728
Sal: Oh, the question is when
am I speaking at TED? (laughter)

01:22:59.728 --> 01:23:00.769
I don't know.

01:23:00.769 --> 01:23:03.129
Actually, I just had a - I don't know.

01:23:03.129 --> 01:23:08.268
If they call me I'll go. (laughter)

01:23:08.268 --> 01:23:09.635
I'll be speaking at Pop -

01:23:09.635 --> 01:23:12.338
Have you all heard of PopTech.

01:23:12.338 --> 01:23:13.519
It's this thing in New Hampshire.

